{"key":"post-6028748","value":"<?xml version=\"1.0\"?>\n<post>\n<id>6028748</id>\n<content>We don't use hay to grow mushrooms indoors.  Hay is harvested from the ends of the stalks, and contains lots of seeds/grain which will contaminate if used in a bulk substrate.  &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We use straw, which doesn't contain seeds.  &lt;br /&gt;RR</content>\n<name>RogerRabbit</name>\n<next>6028783</next>\n<prev>6028524</prev>\n<first>6028483</first>\n<last>6028783</last>\n<when>1157408232</when>\n<utime>09/05/06 01:17 AM</utime>\n</post>"}